<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <meta name="robots" content="noindex, noarchive">
        <meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-cache">
        <meta http-equiv="Expires" content="0">
        <title>AWS: 500 Server Error</title>
        <style>
            @font-face {
                font-family: 'AmazonEmber';
                src: url(data:application/font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff');
                font-weight: normal;
                font-style: normal;
            }

            @font-face {
                font-family: "AmazonEmber";
                src: url(data:application/font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff');
                font-weight: bold;
                font-style: normal;
            }

            body,
            p,
            h1,
            ul,
            li {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }

            body {
                display: flex;
                height: 100vh;
                font-family: "AmazonEmber", Helvetica, Arial, san-serif;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.43;
            }

            body.home-console .is-hidden-home,
            body.service-console .is-hidden-service {
                display: none;
            }

            a {
                color: #0073BB;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

            p {
                margin-bottom: 21px;
            }

            .error-page {
                margin: 16vh auto 0 auto;
                max-width: 90vw;
                max-height: 90vh;
            }

            .error {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                max-width: 690px;
                padding-left: 2px;
            }

            .error__graphic {
                margin: 0 0 16px -2px;
            }

            .error__graphic--500 {
                display: block;
                max-width: 143px;
                max-height: 93px;
            }

            .error__head {
                margin-bottom: 14px;
            }

            .error__foot {
                margin-top: 16px;
            }

            .emphasis {
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .vertical-rhythm {
                margin-bottom: 4px;
            }

            .heading {
                font-weight: normal;
            }

            .heading--h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
                line-height: 1.167;
            }

            .navigation {
                margin-top: 21px;
            }

            .link-list-container {
                margin-bottom: 4px;
            }

            .link-list {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
                list-style: none;
            }

            .link-list>* {
                padding-right: 16px;
            }

            @media screen and (min-width: 400px) {
                .link-list {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
                }

                .link-list-container {
                    max-width: 55%;
                }

                .link-list>* {
                    padding-right: 32px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>

    <body id="page" class="service-console">
        <main class="error-page">
            <div class="error">
                <div class="error__graphic">
                    <svg class="error__graphic--500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <title>AWS 500 Server Error</title>
                        <g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd">
                            <path d="M25.515 91l-.275-72.704" stroke="#AAB7B8" stroke-width="2.52" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <path d="M14.636 10.137c.006 1.73-1.403 3.14-3.147 3.145-1.744.007-3.164-1.391-3.17-3.122-.007-1.73 1.402-3.139 3.146-3.146 1.746-.007 3.165 1.392 3.171 3.123M24.745 10.137c.006 1.73-1.401 3.139-3.147 3.145-1.744.007-3.164-1.391-3.17-3.122-.007-1.732 1.402-3.14 3.147-3.146 1.745-.007 3.165 1.392 3.17 3.123M34.855 10.137c.007 1.73-1.402 3.14-3.148 3.145-1.745.007-3.165-1.391-3.17-3.122-.008-1.73 1.401-3.139 3.147-3.146 1.745-.007 3.165 1.392 3.17 3.123"
                              fill="#AAB7B8" />
                            <path d="M56.336 36.573l44.228-.202M50.018 40.827l-8.812.032-.033-8.743 8.812-.031zM50.018 58.376l-8.812.032-.033-8.743 8.812-.031zM56.336 71.671l48.019-.201M50.018 77.179l-8.812.032-.033-8.743 8.812-.031zM56.336 55.364l42.964-.178M2 17.669h121.31"
                              stroke="#AAB7B8" stroke-width="2.52" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <path d="M141 46.5c0 9.347-7.637 16.923-17.06 16.923-9.42 0-17.058-7.576-17.058-16.923 0-9.346 7.639-16.923 17.059-16.923 9.422 0 17.059 7.577 17.059 16.923z" stroke="#EB5F07" stroke-width="2.52" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <path d="M123.174 23.153l.124-18.633A2.518 2.518 0 0 0 120.77 2H4.527A2.518 2.518 0 0 0 2 4.507v83.986A2.518 2.518 0 0 0 4.527 91h116.255a2.517 2.517 0 0 0 2.527-2.507V69.69" stroke="#AAB7B8" stroke-width="2.52"
                              stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <path d="M125.137 50.124l.408-12.684a3.864 3.864 0 0 0-1.604-.341c-.564 0-1.098.113-1.604.341l.408 12.684h2.392zm-1.196 5.777c.564 0 1.021-.162 1.371-.486.35-.324.524-.74.524-1.247 0-.508-.175-.924-.524-1.248-.35-.323-.807-.485-1.371-.485s-1.02.162-1.371.485c-.35.324-.525.74-.525 1.248 0 .507.175.923.525 1.247.35.324.807.486 1.37.486z"
                              fill="#EB5F07" />
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="error__head">
                    <h1 class="heading heading--h1">
                        <span id="awsConsoleName">Service</span> page is currently unavailable.
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <div class="error__body">
                    <p class="vertical-rhythm" id="dashboard">You can monitor status on the <a href="https://status.aws.amazon.com/" target="_blank">AWS Service Health Dashboard</a>.</p>
                    <div class="navigation is-hidden-service">
                        <p class="vertical-rhythm">You can also get to your AWS services by using these links:</p>
                        <nav class="link-list-container">
                            <ul class="link-list" id="linkList"></ul>
                        </nav>
                        <p>Looking for a different service? Choose any link above, then select a new destination from the <b class="emphasis">Services</b> menu at the top of your screen.</p>
                    </div>
                    <p class="is-hidden-home">To visit a different AWS service page, go to <a href="/console/home" target="_blank">AWS Management Console</a>.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="error__foot">
                    <p class="is-hidden-service">Here are some other common destinations: <a href="/billing/home" target="_blank">Billing</a>, <a href="/billing/home?#/account" target="_blank">Account Details</a>, <a href="/support/home" target="_blank">AWS
                            Support</a>.</p>
                    <p class="is-hidden-home">You can also contact <a href="/support/home" target="_blank">AWS Support</a> for assistance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <script>
            function render(consoles) {
                var body = document.getElementById("page");
                var awsConsoleName = document.getElementById("awsConsoleName");
                var url = window.location.href;
                var serviceIdRegex = new RegExp(/.*?\.(?:com|cn|gov)\/(.+?)(?:\/|$)/);
                var consoleMatcher = serviceIdRegex.exec(url);
                var serviceId = consoleMatcher && consoleMatcher[1] ? consoleMatcher[1] : "";
                serviceId = serviceId.toLowerCase();

                // Set up the list of console links.
                //
                var linkList = document.getElementById("linkList");
                if ( linkList ) {
                    for (var c in consoles) {
                        if (c === "console") continue;

                        var linkItem = document.createElement("li");
                        var linkAnchor = document.createElement("a");
                        var linkText = document.createTextNode(consoles[c].title);

                        linkAnchor.appendChild(linkText);
                        linkAnchor.setAttribute("href", "/" + c + "/home");

                        linkItem.appendChild(linkAnchor);
                        linkList.appendChild(linkItem);
                    }
                }

                // Apply the controller classes to differentiate the layouts and titles.
                //
                if (awsConsoleName && consoles && consoles[serviceId] && consoles[serviceId].hasOwnProperty("title")) {
                    awsConsoleName.textContent = consoles[serviceId].title;
                    if (serviceId === "console") {
                        body.classList.add("home-console");
                        body.classList.remove("service-console");
                    } else {
                        awsConsoleName.textContent += " service";
                    }
                }
            }

            var consoles = {
                "console": {
                    "title": "AWS Management Console Home"
                },
                "ec2": {
                    "title": "EC2"
                },
                "ecs": {
                    "title": "ECS"
                },
                "cloudwatch": {
                    "title": "CloudWatch"
                },
                "lambda": {
                    "title": "Lambda"
                },
                "s3": {
                    "title": "S3"
                },
                "rds": {
                    "title": "RDS"
                },
                "cloudfront": {
                    "title": "CloudFront"
                },
                "route53": {
                    "title": "Route53"
                },
                "iam": {
                    "title": "IAM"
                },
                "vpc": {
                    "title": "VPC"
                },
                "cloudformation": {
                    "title": "CloudFormation"
                },
                "dynamodb": {
                    "title": "DynamoDB"
                }
            };
            render(consoles);
        </script>
    </body>

</html>
